as I will present a little bit later, and understand how these hierarchies and

47
00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:52.760
trajectories are made and sustained.

48
00:02:53.820 --> 00:02:57.480
But then also we want to apply chemical and

49
00:02:57.520 --> 00:03:00.100
genetic perturbation to cell models from these patients,

